-- Los Angeles Buys 560 Megawatts of Solar Power From Sempra, KRoad
-- B y   W i l l   W a d e
-- 2012-12-05T22:14:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/los-angeles-buys-560-megawatts-of-solar-power-from-sempra-kroad.html
The City of Los Angeles agreed to
purchase 560 megawatts of solar energy from projects that  Sempra
Energy (SRE)  and KRoad Power LLC are developing.  The city is expected to sign long-term contracts tomorrow
to buy 210 megawatts of capacity from Sempra’s Copper Mountain
Solar 3 project and 250 megawatts from KRoad’s Moapa Solar
Project, according to an e-mailed statement today from the Los
Angeles mayor’s office.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
 wwade4@bloomberg.net  